These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
House: cottage, colonial, cape-cod, modern
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, family, satire
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the person watching satire movies is the cottage house##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the colonial house is between the person watching family movies and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person watching fantasy movies is the cape-cod house##1
7. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| House         | modern    | colonial  | cottage       | cape-cod     |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | superhero | satire       | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, bluemaster, vegafina
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, domino, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, surfing, swimming
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person playing snooker and the vegafina-smoker##2
5. the person playing snooker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Cigar         | dunhill | bongani    | vegafina  | bluemaster |
| Game   | snooker  | bridge  | poker   | domino    |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | climbing | surfing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, cottage, tower
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, snake, rabbit
1. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the rabbit and the art-deco house##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| House      | art-deco | tower         | farmhouse   | cottage    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Pet   | snake   | ferret        | rabbit      | mouse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, monopoly, chess
City: venice, miami, edinburgh, new-york
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person playing chess##2
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Game   | chess        | snooker   | poker | monopoly |
| City         | edinburgh | venice | miami    | new-york |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, snooker, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, musician, chef, analyst
1. the analyst is between the person playing go and the person playing monopoly##2
2. the analyst is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the writer is on the right of the chef##1
6. the chef is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the analyst is between the chef and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Game   | go | billiard      | monopoly       | snooker   |
| Hobby      | gardening   | puzzles  | woodworking | sudoku     |
| Job      | musician     | analyst | chef        | writer |

