.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different games are played: domino, monopoly, backgammon, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
City: edinburgh, berlin, liverpool, hamburg
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person traveling to liverpool##2
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing domino and the person playing backgammon##2
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game    | backgammon | monopoly  | domino | chess      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| City   | hamburg | edinburgh | berlin | liverpool     |

