.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, russian, australian
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, domino, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is the brazilian##1
2. the person playing domino is the dutch##1
3. the russian is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the russian##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the brazilian and the russian##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Nationality   | russian | australian       | brazilian        | dutch    |
| Game         | monopoly | whist | scrabble  | domino |

