.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, snooker, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, gospel, indie
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fan of r&b is between the owner of the rabbit and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | whist  | bridge | snooker | canasta |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | indie | r&b   | gospel         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

