.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
House: palace, townhouse, art-deco, farmhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, quad-bike, taxi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, salsa, techno
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the palace house##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the townhouse house##1
5. the palace house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the scooter is between the fan of salsa and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| House          | farmhouse  | palace    | art-deco | townhouse       |
| Transport         | taxi | scooter | roller  | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno      | house  | ambient     |

