.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, social-worker, lawyer, manager
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, dancing, gardening
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, guinea-pig, fish
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the lawyer is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the manager##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the manager##1
7. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the owner of the dog is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | lawyer      | manager | social-worker | security-guard |
| Hobby         | gardening   | collecting  | baking | dancing |
| Pet   | fish | dog   | frog | guinea-pig |

