.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
House: tower, futuristic, townhouse, wooden
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, iris, tulip
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, guinea-pig, rat
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the futuristic house##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growsiris##2
4. the person who growsiris is between the owner of the dog and the wooden house##2
5. the person who growsiris is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the goat##1
7. the person who growstulip is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| House    | wooden  | townhouse | tower | futuristic     |
| Flower   | orchid | iris   | tulip  | sunflower    |
| Pet     | goat        | rat       | dog      | guinea-pig |

