.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, soccer, ice-hockey
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, game, bongani
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is basketball##2
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Sport      | soccer  | ice-hockey | badminton  | basketball |
| Cigar        | bongani  | prince      | game        | pall-mall      |

