.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, august, july
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, russian, argentine
1. the person watching disaster movies is the argentine##1
2. the russian is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the russian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the american is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the argentine is on the far right##1
7. the american is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday           | may | july | august    | february   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| Nationality     | indonesian     | american       | russian        | argentine    |

