The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, tram, train
1. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the train is the chaman-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is the security-guard##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the paramedic and the ritmeester-smoker##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the train and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Cigar   | davidoff   | montecristo           | ritmeester         | chaman      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Transport   | tram     | quad-bike         | roller       | train        |

