.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, montecristo, swisher, chaman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, soul
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, colonial, cape-cod
1. the fan of country is the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the swisher-smoker is the fan of funk##1
4. the swisher-smoker is between the fan of rock and the cape-cod house##2
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the ranch-style house is between the colonial house and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar      | montecristo | swisher | bongani   | chaman |
| Music-Genre   | country  | funk    | rock   | soul     |
| House   | cape-cod  | colonial | ranch-style | gothic-revival   |

