.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, july, august
House: victorian, art-deco, colonial, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the colonial house is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the art-deco house is on the right of the colonial house##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Birthday   | january    | november | august           | july |
| House       | victorian | colonial    | art-deco          | cape-cod   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

