.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, purple, turquise, fuchsia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, go, domino
1. the person watching romance movies is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes yellow is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the person playing domino is between the person who likes purple and the person playing scrabble##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Color      | turquise | yellow | purple     | fuchsia   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Game           | scrabble      | domino         | poker | go |

