.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, july, april
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, soul, blues, indie
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
4. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of blues##1
6. the fan of indie is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Birthday         | december        | april  | july | january   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Music-Genre   | classical        | blues     | indie       | soul      |

