.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, strawberry, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, writing, chess, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse, snowboarding, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person eating watermelon and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | watermelon | cabbage | asparagus | strawberry |
| Hobby         | reading       | writing     | chess   | hiking   |
| Sport   | rowing | lacrosse | snowboarding | baseball |

 